program: (PARI) A318749(n, m=n, facs=List([])) = if(1==n, (1!=gcd(Vec(facs))), my(s=0, newfacs); fordiv(n, d, if((d>1)&&(d<=m), newfacs = List(facs); listput(newfacs,d); s += A318749(n/d, d-1, newfacs))); (s)); \\ _Antti Karttunen_, Oct 08 2018
